' NOTES
' ============================================
note top of UpdateAlertPreferencesHandler
  **UPDATE ALERT PREFERENCES FLOW**

  1. Get authenticated user ID from JWT claims
  2. Get area ID from route parameter
  3. Fetch user's subscription for this area
  4. Verify authorization (subscription.UserId == request.UserId)
  5. Update only provided fields (partial update):
     - MinSeverity
     - EnablePush / EnableEmail / EnableSms
     - QuietHoursStart / QuietHoursEnd
  6. Save changes to repository
  7. Return success/failure response

  **API Endpoint:**
  PUT /api/v1/alerts/subscriptions/{areaId}
end note

note bottom of UserAlertSubscription
  **Notification Channels:**
  - Push: FCM push notifications
  - Email: Email notifications
  - SMS: SMS notifications (premium)

  **MinSeverity Values:**
  - info: All alerts
  - caution: Caution and above
  - warning: Warning and critical
  - critical: Critical only

  **Quiet Hours:**
  - Start/End times in UTC
  - User won't receive notifications during these hours
end note

